criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

        Generalized neck-shoulder pain with symptoms provoked by neck postures, neck movement, or
        palpation of the cervical musculature.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  whiplash injury;

          -  previous cervical or thoracic surgery;

          -  cervical radiculopathy or myelopathy;

          -  diagnosis of fibromyalgia syndrome;

          -  having undergone physical therapy in the previous 6 months;

          -  less than 18 or greater than 55 years of age

          -  fear to needles
